See this answer from our archives:

  Saying Numbers Out Loud
  http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/57225.html

In America, at least, it is probably most common to teach students 
not to use "and" in this situation, and that is how I would usually 
say it. But in real life, it doesn't make much difference.

If you have any further questions, feel free to write back.


